<br />
Nestles places Toll House Chocolate Chip Dough Bars right next to the eggs.  The refrigerated dough bars are ready to bake.  They come scored so that the perfect amount of dough for a single cookie can be broken off from the bar.  All you have to do is bake them.<br />
<br />
